snippet.textDisplay: Vikas Tomer Brother... thanks to your father also.... please convey my regards and respect to your father..... love you all..Maan saab also a great writer.... the lyrics of this song are written by him.... snippet.textDisplay: I am from Muktsar, Punjab, India.... I have my Two elder sisters and one elder brother.... all three were born in our Pinds...Chak No-16 and Chak No-6,Near Chishtian Mandi, which was the Tehsil of Zila-Bahawal Pur Punjab, Pakistan... I am the only member of my family,born in Phagwara Punjab after my family shifted after the Partition of our Hindustan by the Siyasat.... I haven't seen my Ancestor's place in Bahawalpur but father, mother,Dada Dadi and all my cousin sisters and brothers"Tarasade han ke Kaash Baba Nanak kirpa kar den te asi kade Apne Buzuragan da Pind maran ton pehlan IKK VAARI DARSHAN KAR SAKIYE....Hun ta Sarkar Kartarpur Corridor vi khol rhiyan ne.... shayad sadi Qismat vich likhia hove Maalik ne...... I offer my whole-hearted Respect, Regards, Mohabbat te Khaloos to all the people of my Ancestor's place Bahawalpur and the whole Awaam of Pakistan....Sat Sri Akal te Salaam to all my brothers and sisters from Satluj Paar....Jeo Punjabio,Guru diyan Mehhran Moujan lavo Ve Punjabio.... love you all Biradar.... please accept it from your Punjabi Veer, unable to kiss the Muqaddass Mitti of Bahawalpur...
